⚠️ COMMON ERRORS + FIXES
Error	Cause	Fix
Bucket already exists	globally unique names	add numbers
Lambda not triggering	trigger missing	reconnect trigger
No logs visible	function not executed	upload file again
Access denied	permission issue	allow IAM permissions
